name: Toy Master
summary:
Early Access

The game is in the early stages, be patient, updates will make you happy soon <3

Welcome to Toy Master, the ultimate construction simulator that lets you enjoy the thrill of opening and putting together new toys and delightful eggs. Dive into a world of excitement with interesting game features and a laid-back atmosphere. Simply unwrap the package, crack open the chocolate egg, and discover the special toy hidden inside.
